    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use</p>\n\n<pre><code>Comparator&lt;File&gt; comparator = Comparator.comparing(File::lastModified); \nCollections.sort(list, comparator.reversed());\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then </p>\n\n<pre><code>.forEach(item -&gt; item.delete());\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4481658,
      "reputation" : 874,
      "user_id" : 3645564,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/4rb96.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "iFederx",
