    "body" : "<p>You can define your Comparator with your own logic like this;</p>\n<pre><code>private static final Comparator&lt;UserResource&gt; sortByLastLogin = (c1, c2) -&gt; {\n    if (Objects.isNull(c1.getLastLoggedin())) {\n        return -1;\n    } else if (Objects.isNull(c2.getLastLoggedin())) {\n        return 1;\n    }\n    return c1.getLastLoggedin().compareTo(c2.getLastLoggedin());\n};   \n</code></pre>\n<p>And use it inside foreach as:</p>\n<pre><code>list.stream()\n     .sorted(sortCredentialsByLastLogin.reversed())\n     .collect(Collectors.toList());\n</code></pre>\n"
